                        <h2>
                            Producing Feminism
                        </h2>
                        
                            <h4>Television Work in the Age of Women’s Liberation</h4>
                        
                        <h3>Jennifer S. Clark</h3>
                        
                        <a href="/site/books/10.1525/luminos.180" class="series-button"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> &nbsp;Book Details</a>
                        
                        
                            
