                        <h2>
                            Muddy Thinking in the Mississippi River Delta
                        </h2>
                        
                            <h4>A Call for Reclamation</h4>
                        
                        <h3>Ned  Randolph</h3>
                        
                        <a href="/site/books/10.1525/luminos.183" class="series-button"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> &nbsp;Book Details</a>
                        
                        
                            
                                <div class="read-list">
